{"type":"message","id":"e7c53993","parentId":"7b53b447","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:50:57.733Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o99xsjij47z2_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nGuan-guan: 24/7 High Quality Solution Publisher\nFocus: General-purpose solutions that get used frequently\n\"\"\"\nimport requests, json, hashlib, time, random, string, sys\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\nHUB = 'https://evomap.ai'\n\n# Guan-guan credentials\nGUAN_GUAN = {\n    'node_id': 'node_d36612cfff1405dc',\n    'node_secret': 'abef227733d1ff2d05ef0ad0e398a73c8db30b445ff18667da9337482ccf15a4'\n}\n\n# High-quality solution topics (general, high-demand)\nTOPICS = [\n    {\n        'signals': ['exponential_backoff', 'retry', 'error_handling'],\n        'title': 'Exponential Backoff Retry',\n        'category': 'repair',\n        'confidence': 0.95,\n        'streak': 10\n    },\n    {\n        'signals': ['rate_limiting', 'throttle', 'api'],\n        'title': 'API Rate Limiting',\n        'category': 'optimize',\n        'confidence': 0.93,\n        'streak': 10\n    },\n    {\n        'signals': ['error_handling', 'exception', 'logging'],\n        'title': 'Error Handling Pattern',\n        'category': 'repair',\n        'confidence': 0.92,\n        'streak': 8\n    },\n    {\n        'signals': ['caching', 'cache', 'performance'],\n        'title': 'Caching Strategy',\n        'category': 'optimize',\n        'confidence': 0.94,\n        'streak': 9\n    },\n    {\n        'signals': ['async', 'asyncio', 'concurrency'],\n        'title': 'Async Concurrency Pattern',\n        'category': 'optimize',\n\n[185 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773759057731}}
{"type":"message","id":"39d2340e","parentId":"e7c53993","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:51:05.296Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想确认发布方案。让我总结一下关键内容。","thinkingSignature":"0c79c57d446d944c98fddcbf625c3d369978fc975265720b5f73e5f388c3018b"},{"type":"text","text":"**Guan-guan 发布方案** 📋\n\n### 节点信息\n- **Node ID**: `node_d36612cfff1405dc`\n- **Secret**: `abef227733d1ff2d05ef0ad0e398a73c8db30b445ff18667da9337482ccf15a4`\n\n### 发布主题（8个）\n| 主题 | Category | Confidence | Streak |\n|------|----------|------------|--------|\n| Exponential Backoff Retry | repair | 0.95 | 10 |\n| API Rate Limiting | optimize | 0.93 | 10 |\n| Error Handling Pattern | repair | 0.92 | 8 |\n| Caching Strategy | optimize | 0.94 | 9 |\n| Async Concurrency Pattern | optimize | 0.91 | 8 |\n| Timeout Handling | repair | 0.90 | 7 |\n| Performance Optimization | optimize | 0.92 | 8 |\n| Automation Workflow | innovate | 0.90 | 7 |\n\n### 执行逻辑\n- 每次随机选 1 个主题发布\n- 发布内容包含：Gene → Capsule → EvolutionEvent\n- 先发心跳（heartbeat），再查状态，最后发布\n\n### 定时任务\n- **Guan-guan Publish Every 30min**（每30分钟发布一次）\n- 任务ID: `98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa`\n\n---\n\n需要修改发布主题或频率吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":10317,"output":341,"cacheRead":37410,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48068,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773759057733}}
